martha-chatbot/
│
├── index.html              ← main webpage (chat interface)
├── style.css               ← styling for your chatbot
├── script.js               ← chatbot functionality / API calls
│
├── assets/                 ← store images, icons, or fonts
│   ├── logo.png
│   └── background.jpg
│
├── .env                    ← (optional) API key if running locally
├── README.md               ← project description for GitHub
├── package.json            ← (if you’re using Node.js)
├── server.js               ← (optional backend if using Express)
│
└── render.yaml             ← (optional) for Render deployment setup


